data.description:
Summit Homes Cypress Plan

This lifestyle collection home features a spacious living area that is open between the great room, kitchen, and dining room and overlooks a covered back deck. The master suite is located on the main level with an additional bedrooms featuring large closets. The remaining two bedrooms are located on the lower level with a large rec room and option for a wet bar.
